01:16:16,708 --> 01:16:19,629
Passed.

743
01:16:19,795 --> 01:16:24,468
Yes, oh... I mean... Ah, I mean...

744
01:16:24,635 --> 01:16:28,473
the cloud has passed away.

745
01:16:28,640 --> 01:16:34,647
Oh, it's gone, it's finished.
The cloud has just really passed.

746
01:16:34,813 --> 01:16:37,358
- Run along, you two.
- Goodbye, Aunt Kate.

747
01:16:37,524 --> 01:16:42,196
- We love you.
- And have a happy, happy honeymoon.

748
